# DeepFake Detection System

## 📌 Overview

DeepFake Detection System is an AI-powered application designed to identify manipulated (fake) and authentic (real) images and videos using Deep Learning techniques. The system helps detect digitally altered media and provides prediction confidence scores for enhanced transparency.

## 🚀 Features

* Detects DeepFake Images
* Detects DeepFake Videos
* Real vs Fake Classification
* Confidence Score Display
* User-Friendly Web Interface
* Frame-Based Video Analysis
* Deep Learning-Based Detection Model
* Fast and Accurate Predictions

## 🛠️ Technologies Used

* Python
* TensorFlow / Keras
* OpenCV
* NumPy
* Flask
* HTML, CSS, JavaScript
* MobileNetV2 (Transfer Learning)

