## 🧠 Model Information

### Image Detection Model

* Architecture: MobileNetV2
* Input Size: 128 × 128
* Binary Classification (Real / Fake)

### Video Detection Model

* Extracts frames from uploaded videos
* Analyzes multiple frames
* Aggregates frame predictions to generate final video classification

## 📊 Dataset

The model was trained using publicly available DeepFake datasets containing both real and manipulated images/videos.

Image Dataset:

* Real Images: 5,000+
* Fake Images: 5,000+

Video Dataset:

* Real Videos: 590+
* Fake Videos: 640+

